msgstr "Gross! A scarecrow filled with human hair! I'll have to admit though, Harry made a pretty decent likeness of himself."

#: 103W009
msgid "I'm not touching that thing. I might get cooties!"
msgstr "I'm not touching that thing. I might get cooties!"

#: 103W010
