msgstr "LOCKED FROM THE OTHER SIDE!"

#: 103W013
msgid "It's some kind of air vent!"
msgstr "It's some kind of air vent!"

#: 103W014
msgid "I'm not touching that! It's covered with bird doo-doo!"
msgstr "I'm not touching that! It's covered with bird doo-doo!"

#: 103W015
msgid "I can't use that!"
msgstr "I can't use that!"

#: 104W001
