msgstr "It's a good thing those creepy aliens don't want to be taken to my leader. If Mayor Gus got involved, we'd be burger meat for sure!"

#: 104W003
msgid "Mayor Gus's door is always open, even though I think he should be locked up."
msgstr "Mayor Gus's door is always open, even though I think he should be locked up."

#: 104W004
msgid "If those slobbery aliens turned me into a burger, they could use Stolie for the pickle!"
msgstr "If those slobbery aliens turned me into a burger, they could use Stolie for the pickle!"

#: 104W005
msgid "Nah, Stolie wouldn't want that."
msgstr "Nah, Stolie wouldn't want that."

#: 104W006
