msgstr "Ugh, that fountain gives me the willies ever since I caught Stolie bathing in it."

#: 104W007
msgid "I don't think so."
msgstr "I don't think so."

#: 104W008
msgid "I can't get into the impound yard that way. If the razor wire doesn't get me, old peg leg will."
msgstr "I can't get into the impound yard that way. If the razor wire doesn't get me, old peg leg will."

