msgid "I wonder if the major domo can help me."
msgstr "I wonder if the major domo can help me."

#: 105W003
msgid "Complaints department? Well, I've sure got a few things I'd like to get off my chest."
msgstr "Complaints department? Well, I've sure got a few things I'd like to get off my chest."

