msgid "Even with this sturdy metal fence between us, I don't like being this close to that mongrel."
msgstr "Even with this sturdy metal fence between us, I don't like being this close to that mongrel."

#: 106W009
msgid "I'm not climbing that!"
msgstr "I'm not climbing that!"

