msgstr "It's dangerous walking around in here with Kibble on the floor."

#: 600W013
msgid "Oh, that'll help."
msgstr "Oh, that'll help."

#: 600W014
msgid "I think they are angry enough already."
msgstr "I think they are angry enough already."

#: 601F001
msgid "You are a lot heavier than you look, human."
msgstr "You are a lot heavier than you look, human."

#: 601F003
msgid "Sorry, boss. Didn't mean to bruise our dinner."
msgstr "Sorry, boss. Didn't mean to bruise our dinner."

#: 601W001
msgid "Whoa!"
msgstr "Whoa!"

#: 601W002
msgid "Um... what's my gerbil cage doing here?"
msgstr "Um... what's my gerbil cage doing here?"

