msgid "Easy, you idiot! We might be eatin' them later!"
msgstr "Easy, you idiot! We might be eatin' them later!"

#: 601Z005
msgid "Alright, human. You squeaked by the first test, but that was the easy part. Now we start testing your higher mental functions, beginning with your survival instincts!"
msgstr "Alright, human. You squeaked by the first test, but that was the easy part. Now we start testing your higher mental functions, beginning with your survival instincts!"

#: 601Z006
msgid "You about to find out!"
msgstr "You about to find out!"

