msgstr "Aha! There's the door! I'll be out of here in no time!"

#: 602W004
msgid "Well, so much for those nasty robo-rodents. No wait, this one's still kickin'!"
msgstr "Well, so much for those nasty robo-rodents. No wait, this one's still kickin'!"

#: 602W005
msgid "Oh no... I spoke too soon!"
msgstr "Oh no... I spoke too soon!"

#: 602W006
msgid "Such fussy eaters. They've hardly touched their food at all."
msgstr "Such fussy eaters. They've hardly touched their food at all."

#: 602W007
msgid "Well, that's not going anywhere. It's attached to the cage."
msgstr "Well, that's not going anywhere. It's attached to the cage."

#: 602W009
msgid "Gerbil chow. Best gerbil food money can buy. Keeps their coats nice and shiny."
msgstr "Gerbil chow. Best gerbil food money can buy. Keeps their coats nice and shiny."

#: 602W010
msgid "I already have some kibble."
msgstr "I already have some kibble."

#: 602W011
msgid "I don't have any kibble."
msgstr "I don't have any kibble."

#: 602W012X
msgid "Hardest ball bearings!"
msgstr "Hardest ball bearings!"

#: 602W012Y
msgid "Pfft, pfft..."
msgstr "Pfft, pfft..."

#: 602W012Z
msgid "Eugh, tastes like ball bearings too. How do they eat this junk?"
msgstr "Eugh, tastes like ball bearings too. How do they eat this junk?"

#: 602W013
msgid "Winona hid behind that wheel for weeks when Charlie and Louie were feeling frisky last spring. Oh, memories."
msgstr "Winona hid behind that wheel for weeks when Charlie and Louie were feeling frisky last spring. Oh, memories."

#: 602W014
msgid "Yeah, right!"
msgstr "Yeah, right!"

#: 602W015
msgid "Alright, the door is opening. And those space creeps thought I wouldn't get out of here."
msgstr "Alright, the door is opening. And those space creeps thought I wouldn't get out of here."

#: 602W016A
msgid "He... He... He..."
msgstr "He... He... He..."

#: 602W016B
msgid "HEH HEH HEH HEH"
msgstr "HEH HEH HEH HEH"

#: 602W016C
msgid "Ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha."
msgstr "Ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha."

#: 602W016D
msgid "Ah, ah, ah, ah..."
msgstr "Ah, ah, ah, ah..."

#: 602W017A
msgid "Phew! I should have worn my sweats!"
msgstr "Phew! I should have worn my sweats!"

#: 602W017B
msgid "Man, I'm way out of shape."
msgstr "Man, I'm way out of shape."

#: 602W017C
msgid "Oh, this is really tiring!"
msgstr "Oh, this is really tiring!"

#: 602W017D
msgid "Man, what a workout!"
msgstr "Man, what a workout!"

#: 602W017E
msgid "Oh, my gym teacher is right. My sweat does have a pleasant odor."
msgstr "Oh, my gym teacher is right. My sweat does have a pleasant odor."

#: 602W017F
msgid "This is getting nowhere fast."
msgstr "This is getting nowhere fast."

#: 602W017G
msgid "Phew!"
msgstr "Phew!"

#: 602W018
msgid "Uh-oh."
msgstr "Uh-oh."

#: 602W019
msgid "HUAH!"
msgstr "HUAH!"

#: 602W020
