msgstr "Hmm, I guess this is going to be tougher than I thought. There's gotta be a way to keep that door open."

#: 602W021
msgid "Hmm... that's odd. Some kind of generator is connected to the exercise wheel."
msgstr "Hmm... that's odd. Some kind of generator is connected to the exercise wheel."

#: 602W022
msgid "The generator seems to power the magnet when the exercise wheel is turning."
msgstr "The generator seems to power the magnet when the exercise wheel is turning."

#: 602W023
msgid "I can't reach it."
msgstr "I can't reach it."

#: 602W024
msgid "Hmm... I never noticed a magnet up there before, and it seems to be connected to that generator thingy."
msgstr "Hmm... I never noticed a magnet up there before, and it seems to be connected to that generator thingy."

#: 602W025
msgid "The magnet raises the door while the generator is running."
msgstr "The magnet raises the door while the generator is running."

#: 602W026
msgid "I'll just open this door and I am out of here!"
msgstr "I'll just open this door and I am out of here!"

#: 602W027
msgid "Hmm. Wheel turns, door opens. Wheel stops turning, door closes again."
msgstr "Hmm. Wheel turns, door opens. Wheel stops turning, door closes again."

#: 602W028
msgid "That door is too heavy to lift."
msgstr "That door is too heavy to lift."

#: 602W029
