msgstr "Ah, don't worry about them. They won't get far in that little runabout. I'm glad he's out of my hair for a little while."

#: 709A002
msgid "Well, I guess it's time you learned. First, let me launch the space bully."
msgstr "Well, I guess it's time you learned. First, let me launch the space bully."

#: 709A003
msgid "There! Okay, now push that button over there."
msgstr "There! Okay, now push that button over there."

#: 709A004
msgid "No, no, not that!"
msgstr "No, no, not that!"

#: 709W001
msgid "THEY'RE GETTING AWAY!"
msgstr "THEY'RE GETTING AWAY!"

#: 709W002
msgid "This one?"
msgstr "This one?"

#: 801W001
msgid "Charlie! Louie! Winona! Come and get it! Delicious, nutritious rodent kibble! Yum yum!"
msgstr "Charlie! Louie! Winona! Come and get it! Delicious, nutritious rodent kibble! Yum yum!"

#: 801W002
msgid "Oh, what the..."
msgstr "Oh, what the..."

#: 802F001
msgid "Greetings from all the nice folks in the Protein Procurement Division at Orion Burger, Incorporated!"
msgstr "Greetings from all the nice folks in the Protein Procurement Division at Orion Burger, Incorporated!"

#: 802F002
msgid "Ah!"
msgstr "Ah!"

#: 802F003
msgid "Urgh!"
msgstr "Urgh!"

#: 802F004
msgid "The GeoKronoSync Unit!"
msgstr "The GeoKronoSync Unit!"

#: 802F005
msgid "Oh dear, this means that the human's memory wasn't erased!"
msgstr "Oh dear, this means that the human's memory wasn't erased!"

#: 802F006
msgid "Well, I know I've sent him back, but I can't exactly tell where. Or when. Could be next week. Could be last year. Who knows?"
msgstr "Well, I know I've sent him back, but I can't exactly tell where. Or when. Could be next week. Could be last year. Who knows?"

#: 802F007
msgid "Oh, the boss isn't gonna like this one bit. I'm deep in gastrointestinal expulsion material!"
msgstr "Oh, the boss isn't gonna like this one bit. I'm deep in gastrointestinal expulsion material!"

#: 802F009
msgid "I'll be back for you in a few minutes, so don't go anywhere."
msgstr "I'll be back for you in a few minutes, so don't go anywhere."

#: 803F001
msgid "Ups-a-daisy!"
msgstr "Ups-a-daisy!"

#: 803F002
msgid "Oh, you're such a headache when you do that."
msgstr "Oh, you're such a headache when you do that."

#: 803F003
msgid "Aye, aye, boss!"
msgstr "Aye, aye, boss!"

#: 803F004
msgid "Ahem. Come on, you!"
msgstr "Ahem. Come on, you!"

#: 803F005
msgid "The results are accurate, boss. He passed fair and square."
msgstr "The results are accurate, boss. He passed fair and square."

#: 803W001
msgid "Whoa! What a trip! What happened?"
msgstr "Whoa! What a trip! What happened?"

#: 803Z001
msgid "Well, it's about time!"
msgstr "Well, it's about time!"

#: 803Z002
msgid "Sheesh! Scrawnier than I would have hoped. Getting paid by the Tarakilo for these second-growth planets is no way to make a living!"
msgstr "Sheesh! Scrawnier than I would have hoped. Getting paid by the Tarakilo for these second-growth planets is no way to make a living!"

#: 803Z003
msgid "Well, what are you waiting for, you flying jello mold? Strap them down, I don't have all day!"
msgstr "Well, what are you waiting for, you flying jello mold? Strap them down, I don't have all day!"

#: 803Z004
msgid "Send this wretched mess of protoplasm back to his planet. I'll hose him up with the rest of those ignorant earthlings!"
msgstr "Send this wretched mess of protoplasm back to his planet. I'll hose him up with the rest of those ignorant earthlings!"

#: 803Z005
msgid "AND THEN CLEAN UP THIS MESS!"
msgstr "AND THEN CLEAN UP THIS MESS!"

#: 803Z006
msgid "What happened? WHAT HAPPENED?!"
msgstr "What happened? WHAT HAPPENED?!"

#: 803Z007
msgid "YOU PASSED MY TEST! THAT'S WHAT HAPPENED!"
msgstr "YOU PASSED MY TEST! THAT'S WHAT HAPPENED!"

#: 803Z008
msgid "Cool. How those puny neurons conducted that pulse, I'll never know. There must be a malfunction in the system."
msgstr "Cool. How those puny neurons conducted that pulse, I'll never know. There must be a malfunction in the system."

#: 803Z009
msgid "Fair and square. Fair and square! Don't ever use those words around me again! Now throw them in the break while I prepare the next test. Fair and square."
msgstr "Fair and square. Fair and square! Don't ever use those words around me again! Now throw them in the break while I prepare the next test. Fair and square."

#: 804F002
msgid "Is that good, boss?"
msgstr "Is that good, boss?"

#: 804F003
msgid "Okay, boss. Everything's set to go."
msgstr "Okay, boss. Everything's set to go."

#: 804F004
msgid "Are you ready?"
msgstr "Are you ready?"

#: 804Z001
msgid "A hundred billion Neurosites!"
msgstr "A hundred billion Neurosites!"

#: 804Z002
msgid "It's pitiful!"
msgstr "It's pitiful!"

#: 804Z003
msgid "I'm amazed that this creature was able to crawl out of the primordial ooze with such a sorry excuse for a brain."
msgstr "I'm amazed that this creature was able to crawl out of the primordial ooze with such a sorry excuse for a brain."

#: 805W001
msgid "OUGLELELELELELE-"
msgstr "OUGLELELELELELE-"

#: 806F002
msgid "INCREDIBLE!"
msgstr "INCREDIBLE!"

#: 806F003
msgid "His neurosynaptic bandwidth is right off the scale for a Gamma class life form."
msgstr "His neurosynaptic bandwidth is right off the scale for a Gamma class life form."

#: 806W001
msgid "No!"
msgstr "No!"

#: 806W001A
msgid "Ha! No!"
msgstr "Ha! No!"

#: 806W001C
msgid "OOOH!"
msgstr "OOOH!"

#: 806W001D
msgid "NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO"
msgstr "NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO"

#: 806W001E
msgid "Waaaaaaaaaaaaaaah!"
msgstr "Waaaaaaaaaaaaaaah!"

#: 806W001F
msgid "OOOOOHOOHOOHOHOHOH!"
msgstr "OOOOOHOOHOOHOHOHOH!"

#: 806W001G
msgid "Waaah!"
msgstr "Waaah!"

#: 806Z001
msgid "What a huge surprise! His minuscule brain barely conducts at all!"
msgstr "What a huge surprise! His minuscule brain barely conducts at all!"

#: 806Z002
msgid "Gah-hah-hah!"
msgstr "Gah-hah-hah!"

#: 80N0101
msgid "Why, neurosynaptic testing, of course!"
msgstr "Why, neurosynaptic testing, of course!"

#: 80N0201
msgid "Oh, how rude of me. I am Flummox, and this is Senior Protein Procurement Agent Slarg."
msgstr "Oh, how rude of me. I am Flummox, and this is Senior Protein Procurement Agent Slarg."

#: 80N0202
msgid "That's right! We're purveyors of premium protein for Orion Burger, Incorporated, the largest fast-food chain in the entire galaxy! Your planet has been identified as a candidate for protein harvesting!"
msgstr "That's right! We're purveyors of premium protein for Orion Burger, Incorporated, the largest fast-food chain in the entire galaxy! Your planet has been identified as a candidate for protein harvesting!"

#: 80N0203
msgid "You are in geosynchronous orbit directly above your Earth settlement."
msgstr "You are in geosynchronous orbit directly above your Earth settlement."

#: 80N0204
msgid "We're testing you to find out if Earthlings are intelligent or not. You see, intelligent life is an extremely scarce resource in the universe. We wouldn't want to grind it up in our Orion burgers by accident, would we, boss?"
msgstr "We're testing you to find out if Earthlings are intelligent or not. You see, intelligent life is an extremely scarce resource in the universe. We wouldn't want to grind it up in our Orion burgers by accident, would we, boss?"

#: 80N0205
msgid "No, we don't test leaders anymore. They were failing our intelligence tests so badly that we had to switch to randomly selected test specimens. So, you're our randomly selected Earthling!"
msgstr "No, we don't test leaders anymore. They were failing our intelligence tests so badly that we had to switch to randomly selected test specimens. So, you're our randomly selected Earthling!"

#: 80N0206
msgid "That's neurosynaptic testing, bucko! Quite simply, we're going to apply a simulated nerve impulse to your cerebral cortex and measure how much juice your primitive little noodle can handle."
msgstr "That's neurosynaptic testing, bucko! Quite simply, we're going to apply a simulated nerve impulse to your cerebral cortex and measure how much juice your primitive little noodle can handle."

#: 80N0207
msgid "They're electrodes, you ninny! Can't apply simulated nerve impulses without electrodes!"
msgstr "They're electrodes, you ninny! Can't apply simulated nerve impulses without electrodes!"

#: 80N0208
msgid "Just relax your nerve fibers and conduct as much of the impulse as you possibly can."
msgstr "Just relax your nerve fibers and conduct as much of the impulse as you possibly can."

#: 80N0209
msgid "Hello! Are you paying any attention at all? If you fail, we harvest your planet!"
msgstr "Hello! Are you paying any attention at all? If you fail, we harvest your planet!"

#: 80N0301
msgid "That's the general idea, human!"
msgstr "That's the general idea, human!"

#: 80N0401
msgid "Oh joy, Flummox! We found ourselves a complete idiot!"
msgstr "Oh joy, Flummox! We found ourselves a complete idiot!"

#: 80N0402
msgid "Yeah! Imagine being in geosynchronous orbit without a spaceship! Ha ha ha ha ha! Oh, that's rich!"
msgstr "Yeah! Imagine being in geosynchronous orbit without a spaceship! Ha ha ha ha ha! Oh, that's rich!"

#: 80N0501
msgid "Oh, of course not! That would be just too... terrible!"
msgstr "Oh, of course not! That would be just too... terrible!"

#: 80N0701
msgid "Gee, uh, I don't know. Does it hurt, boss?"
msgstr "Gee, uh, I don't know. Does it hurt, boss?"

#: 80N0702
msgid "With any luck at all, it'll be excruciating!"
msgstr "With any luck at all, it'll be excruciating!"

#: 80N0901
msgid "Speaking of harvesting, Flammocks, get on with the test!"
msgstr "Speaking of harvesting, Flammocks, get on with the test!"

#: 80N0902
msgid "Okay, boss!"
msgstr "Okay, boss!"

#: 80P0101
msgid "Um, am I ready for what?"
msgstr "Um, am I ready for what?"

#: 80P0201
msgid "Who are you guys?"
msgstr "Who are you guys?"

#: 80P0202
msgid "Protein Procurement Agent?"
msgstr "Protein Procurement Agent?"

#: 80P0203
msgid "Where am I?"
msgstr "Where am I?"

#: 80P0204
msgid "Why are you testing me?"
msgstr "Why are you testing me?"

#: 80P0205
msgid "Don't you want me to take you to my leader?"
msgstr "Don't you want me to take you to my leader?"

#: 80P0206
msgid "Um, what is neuro... whatchamacallit, testing?"
msgstr "Um, what is neuro... whatchamacallit, testing?"

#: 80P0207
msgid "What are these things on my head?"
msgstr "What are these things on my head?"

#: 80P0208
msgid "What do I have to do to pass this test?"
msgstr "What do I have to do to pass this test?"

#: 80P0209
msgid "What happens if I fail the test?"
msgstr "What happens if I fail the test?"

#: 80P0301
msgid "So, uh, you guys are gonna make hamburgers out of me?"
msgstr "So, uh, you guys are gonna make hamburgers out of me?"

#: 80P0401
msgid "You mean this is a spaceship?"
msgstr "You mean this is a spaceship?"

#: 80P0601
msgid "Haha, lucky me!"
msgstr "Haha, lucky me!"

#: 80P0701
msgid "Simulated nerve impulse? Um... Will it hurt?"
msgstr "Simulated nerve impulse? Um... Will it hurt?"

#: 80P0801
msgid "That's what I was afraid of!"
msgstr "That's what I was afraid of!"

#: 80P0903
msgid "Be gentle!"
msgstr "Be gentle!"

#: 81N0101
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr "What do you want?"

#: 81N0201
msgid "Headache? Yeah, sure. I got something for your headache."
msgstr "Headache? Yeah, sure. I got something for your headache."

#: 81N0202
msgid "It's an Abduct-A-Tron Model 2000, I think. I'm going to use it to send you back to Earth, to the exact time and place that you were abducted from."
msgstr "It's an Abduct-A-Tron Model 2000, I think. I'm going to use it to send you back to Earth, to the exact time and place that you were abducted from."

#: 81N0203
msgid "Don't be silly, you failed the test. Of course you are going to beat Burger Meat, you and the rest of your sorry planet."
msgstr "Don't be silly, you failed the test. Of course you are going to beat Burger Meat, you and the rest of your sorry planet."

#: 81N0204
msgid "What's to talk about? I'm starving!"
msgstr "What's to talk about? I'm starving!"

#: 81N0205
msgid "Oh, that? That's just a neutrino pulse gun. I fire it at your brain, and it erases your chartreuse memory. Nothing to get worked up about."
msgstr "Oh, that? That's just a neutrino pulse gun. I fire it at your brain, and it erases your chartreuse memory. Nothing to get worked up about."

#: 81N0206
msgid "Boy, you're just full of questions, aren't you? Well, for your information, I have to erase your memory. It's standard abduction protocol. You see, we send you back to the exact time and place we snatched you from, with no memory of your abduction. That way, you don't know you were gone, and no one else knows you were gone either. Pretty clever, don't you think?"
msgstr "Boy, you're just full of questions, aren't you? Well, for your information, I have to erase your memory. It's standard abduction protocol. You see, we send you back to the exact time and place we snatched you from, with no memory of your abduction. That way, you don't know you were gone, and no one else knows you were gone either. Pretty clever, don't you think?"

#: 81N0301
msgid "Don't you think I have better things to do than lug you all the way back down to the cargo hold? I'm sending you back to Earth, so that we can harvest you with the rest of your pathetic species."
msgstr "Don't you think I have better things to do than lug you all the way back down to the cargo hold? I'm sending you back to Earth, so that we can harvest you with the rest of your pathetic species."

#: 81N0401
msgid "Of course, none of this matters a whole lot in your case. You know, with your planet about to be harvested and all."
msgstr "Of course, none of this matters a whole lot in your case. You know, with your planet about to be harvested and all."

#: 81N0402
msgid "Alright, we're ready to go."
msgstr "Alright, we're ready to go."

#: 81N0403
msgid "On behalf of all the nice folks in Orion Burger's Protein Procurement Division, I would like to thank you for your cooperation during our testing procedures. Have a super day!"
msgstr "On behalf of all the nice folks in Orion Burger's Protein Procurement Division, I would like to thank you for your cooperation during our testing procedures. Have a super day!"

#: 81P0101
msgid "Ah, excuse me."
msgstr "Ah, excuse me."

#: 81P0201
msgid "Do you have anything for a headache?"
msgstr "Do you have anything for a headache?"

#: 81P0202
msgid "What is this thing that I'm in?"
msgstr "What is this thing that I'm in?"

#: 81P0203
msgid "Phew! I thought I was going to be burger meat!"
msgstr "Phew! I thought I was going to be burger meat!"

#: 81P0204
msgid "Uh, c-couldn't we talk this over?"
msgstr "Uh, c-couldn't we talk this over?"

#: 81P0205
msgid "Why is that gun thingy pointing at my head?"
msgstr "Why is that gun thingy pointing at my head?"

#: 81P0206
msgid "Why are you erasing my memory?"
msgstr "Why are you erasing my memory?"

#: 81P0301
msgid "So, why are you sending me back to Earth, then?"
msgstr "So, why are you sending me back to Earth, then?"

#: 81P0401
msgid "I suppose so."
msgstr "I suppose so."

#: 81P0402
msgid "I suppose not."
msgstr "I suppose not."

#: 82N0101
msgid "That's funny. I don't feel so great either. I must be coming down with something."
msgstr "That's funny. I don't feel so great either. I must be coming down with something."

#: 82N0201
msgid "I think so. No, wait. I seem to have misplaced my legs... and my nose."
msgstr "I think so. No, wait. I seem to have misplaced my legs... and my nose."

#: 82N0202
msgid "No... uh... what happened?"
msgstr "No... uh... what happened?"

#: 82N0203
msgid "Uh, I'm... I'm really confused right now."
msgstr "Uh, I'm... I'm really confused right now."

#: 82N0204
msgid "Oh, yeah. You're Swarg, my wonderful boss."
msgstr "Oh, yeah. You're Swarg, my wonderful boss."

#: 82N0205
msgid "You forgot where the meat blocker is? You must be a little confused too. Follow me, boss."
msgstr "You forgot where the meat blocker is? You must be a little confused too. Follow me, boss."

#: 82N0206
msgid "Human? I don't know. I guess he got away from me somehow."
msgstr "Human? I don't know. I guess he got away from me somehow."

#: 82N0207
msgid "Oh, lost your keys? I'm having one of those days too, boss."
msgstr "Oh, lost your keys? I'm having one of those days too, boss."

#: 82N0301
msgid "Oh, don't worry about that. I'll clean it up later, boss."
msgstr "Oh, don't worry about that. I'll clean it up later, boss."

#: 82P0101
msgid "You're looking pretty out of it, Flummox."
msgstr "You're looking pretty out of it, Flummox."

#: 82P0201
msgid "Can you stand on one leg and touch your nose?"
msgstr "Can you stand on one leg and touch your nose?"

#: 82P0202
msgid "You look lost. Do you know where you are?"
msgstr "You look lost. Do you know where you are?"

#: 82P0203
msgid "Do you know who you are?"
msgstr "Do you know who you are?"

#: 82P0204
msgid "Do you know who I am?"
msgstr "Do you know who I am?"

#: 82P0205
msgid "I'm hungry. Where is my meat locker?"
msgstr "I'm hungry. Where is my meat locker?"

#: 82P0206
msgid "Where is the human? Y-you moron!"
msgstr "Where is the human? Y-you moron!"

#: 82P0207
msgid "How do you get these big doors to open?"
msgstr "How do you get these big doors to open?"

#: 82P0301
msgid "I'm not sure, but you sure made a mess of the Abduct-A-Tron."
msgstr "I'm not sure, but you sure made a mess of the Abduct-A-Tron."

#: 82P0401
msgid "BOSS!"
msgstr "BOSS!"

#: 83N0101
msgid "I didn't think I'd see you again. How did you escape?"
msgstr "I didn't think I'd see you again. How did you escape?"

#: 83N0201
msgid "I will be, after I thaw out a bit more."
msgstr "I will be, after I thaw out a bit more."

#: 83N0202
msgid "He went to the bridge to harvest your planet. Uh... why are we whispering?"
msgstr "He went to the bridge to harvest your planet. Uh... why are we whispering?"

#: 83N0203
msgid "I wish I could, but I can hardly move right now, except to shiver. You better go on without me."
msgstr "I wish I could, but I can hardly move right now, except to shiver. You better go on without me."

#: 83N0204
msgid "Every one of these creatures is from a planet that's already been harvested. And I'll bet that they're all intelligent life forms."
msgstr "Every one of these creatures is from a planet that's already been harvested. And I'll bet that they're all intelligent life forms."

#: 83N0205
msgid "How are you going to stop him?"
msgstr "How are you going to stop him?"

#: 83N0301
msgid "You're kidding! That's amazing!"
msgstr "You're kidding! That's amazing!"

#: 83N0401
msgid "Yeah, no fooling. And I would have been Zlog's lunch if you hadn't saved me."
msgstr "Yeah, no fooling. And I would have been Zlog's lunch if you hadn't saved me."

#: 83N0501
msgid "I... I see. Well, good luck!"
msgstr "I... I see. Well, good luck!"

#: 83P0102
msgid "Well, things were a little dicey at first, but then I took a moment to reflect on my situation, and well, a solution just sort of hit me."
msgstr "Well, things were a little dicey at first, but then I took a moment to reflect on my situation, and well, a solution just sort of hit me."

#: 83P0201
msgid "Are you okay?"
msgstr "Are you okay?"

#: 83P0202
msgid "Which way did Zlar go?"
msgstr "Which way did Zlar go?"

#: 83P0203
msgid "Will you help me stop the harvest?"
msgstr "Will you help me stop the harvest?"

#: 83P0204
msgid "Ugh! What a creepy place this is!"
msgstr "Ugh! What a creepy place this is!"

#: 83P0205
msgid "Take care, Astral! I'm gonna stop Zlarg now!"
msgstr "Take care, Astral! I'm gonna stop Zlarg now!"

#: 83P0301
msgid "I don't want Bubblebutt to hear us. He thinks that I'm Zlarg."
msgstr "I don't want Bubblebutt to hear us. He thinks that I'm Zlarg."

#: 83P0401
msgid "Unbelievable! I guess that gluttonous green glob likes to keep a few choice cuts aside for himself!"
msgstr "Unbelievable! I guess that gluttonous green glob likes to keep a few choice cuts aside for himself!"

#: 83P0501
msgid "I haven't thought that far ahead, but I'm sure that something will come to me."
msgstr "I haven't thought that far ahead, but I'm sure that something will come to me."

#: 84N0201
msgid "Oh yeah, yeah, you'd have to go clear over the... clear over the Boonsville to find quality like this. Straight!"
msgstr "Oh yeah, yeah, you'd have to go clear over the... clear over the Boonsville to find quality like this. Straight!"

#: 84N0202
msgid "Is that so? Well, then you sir, you make some of the finest swill in the state."
msgstr "Is that so? Well, then you sir, you make some of the finest swill in the state."

#: 84N0203
msgid "Well, no wonder it's so good! I gotta get me a case of this school, isn't it, bro?"
msgstr "Well, no wonder it's so good! I gotta get me a case of this school, isn't it, bro?"

#: 84N0204
msgid "Yeah, yeah, tell us, what's your secret ingredient, Elminer?"
msgstr "Yeah, yeah, tell us, what's your secret ingredient, Elminer?"

#: 84N0205
msgid "I could be happier. Actually, I'm kind of concerned about my new best buddy, Elmer. He's a little down in the dumps right now. I won't be happy until I figure out a way to lift his spirits, you know what I mean?"
msgstr "I could be happier. Actually, I'm kind of concerned about my new best buddy, Elmer. He's a little down in the dumps right now. I won't be happy until I figure out a way to lift his spirits, you know what I mean?"

#: 84N0206
msgid "Ah, you and your space aliens. And the kid says he doesn't drink. Yeah, I believe that."
msgstr "Ah, you and your space aliens. And the kid says he doesn't drink. Yeah, I believe that."

#: 84N0207
msgid "You can go away, and leave us alone!"
msgstr "You can go away, and leave us alone!"

#: 84N0208
msgid "Of course not, Island Stealer. We ain't got no still."
msgstr "Of course not, Island Stealer. We ain't got no still."

#: 84N0209
msgid "I'll see you later, Wilbur!"
msgstr "I'll see you later, Wilbur!"

#: 84N0210
msgid "Good riddance, the island stealer!"
msgstr "Good riddance, the island stealer!"

#: 84N0301
msgid "This is Bonesville, ya twit!"
msgstr "This is Bonesville, ya twit!"

#: 84N0302
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr "Yes?"

#: 84N0303
msgid "Boy, I must be even more looped than I thought. And I knew I was sort of looped."
msgstr "Boy, I must be even more looped than I thought. And I knew I was sort of looped."

#: 84N0401
msgid "Glad you like it, doody!"
msgstr "Glad you like it, doody!"

#: 84N0402
msgid "The name is Stolie-um-um-er."
msgstr "The name is Stolie-um-um-er."

#: 84N0501
msgid "You can't. That's the last bottle, and I ain't got my still no more. This little hoolum swiped it for me."
msgstr "You can't. That's the last bottle, and I ain't got my still no more. This little hoolum swiped it for me."

#: 84N0502
msgid "Say it ain't so, Wilbur!"
msgstr "Say it ain't so, Wilbur!"

#: 84N0601
msgid "Rotten Cabbage!"
msgstr "Rotten Cabbage!"

#: 84N0602
msgid "Oh, well, that explains the exquisite bouquet."
msgstr "Oh, well, that explains the exquisite bouquet."

#: 84N0701
msgid "Exactly why do you want to make us happy? What do you say? Kind of a good samaritan?"
msgstr "Exactly why do you want to make us happy? What do you say? Kind of a good samaritan?"

#: 84N0702
msgid "If you ask me, you're a jerk!"
msgstr "If you ask me, you're a jerk!"

#: 84N0703
msgid "Why are you so mean to the boy?"
msgstr "Why are you so mean to the boy?"

#: 84N0704
msgid "Cuz he screwed some cockamamie deed in my face and scraped everything I own. Now I got no island, no mine, no house, no steel, no nothing."
msgstr "Cuz he screwed some cockamamie deed in my face and scraped everything I own. Now I got no island, no mine, no house, no steel, no nothing."

#: 84N0705
msgid "Say it ain't so, Wilbur!"
msgstr "Say it ain't so, Wilbur!"

#: 84N0801
msgid "Oh, he did, did he?"
msgstr "Oh, he did, did he?"

#: 84N0802
msgid "Well, that's no excuse, Wilbur. If you really wanted to save the world, you'd let us make some more of that... that heavenly nectar."
msgstr "Well, that's no excuse, Wilbur. If you really wanted to save the world, you'd let us make some more of that... that heavenly nectar."

#: 84N0901
msgid "Hey! Where did the town hall go?"
msgstr "Hey! Where did the town hall go?"

#: 84N0902
msgid "I blasted it to smithereens! That's where it went!"
msgstr "I blasted it to smithereens! That's where it went!"

#: 84N1001
msgid "You know, I bet if we bottle that stuff and put like a nice yuppie label on it, we can make zillions! Hey, what do you say? You can be the broom-meister, huh? And I'll be the brains!"
msgstr "You know, I bet if we bottle that stuff and put like a nice yuppie label on it, we can make zillions! Hey, what do you say? You can be the broom-meister, huh? And I'll be the brains!"

#: 84N1002
msgid "Great idea, brains! Except for one small thing. We ain't got no still!"
msgstr "Great idea, brains! Except for one small thing. We ain't got no still!"

#: 84N1003
msgid "Oh, yeah. Well, I didn't say I had all the details of the work, so give me a break, okay?"
msgstr "Oh, yeah. Well, I didn't say I had all the details of the work, so give me a break, okay?"

#: 84P0201
msgid "Is Elmo's rotgut really that good?"
msgstr "Is Elmo's rotgut really that good?"

#: 84P0202
msgid "Elmo made that hooch himself!"
msgstr "Elmo made that hooch himself!"

#: 84P0203
msgid "Elmo aged that hooch for an entire two weeks!"
msgstr "Elmo aged that hooch for an entire two weeks!"

#: 84P0204
msgid "What is that hooch made from?"
msgstr "What is that hooch made from?"

#: 84P0205
msgid "Are you happy, Stolie?"
msgstr "Are you happy, Stolie?"

#: 84P0206
msgid "Space Aliens said I have to make you guys happy!"
msgstr "Space Aliens said I have to make you guys happy!"

#: 84P0207
