msgstr "Oh, I really don't know. But I suppose if I had a proper anniversary gift for her, I wouldn't be in this mess in the first place."

#: 86N0507
msgid "What, you daft? I can't just give her any old thing. You know, it is our leather anniversary after all. Why, it would have to be something, you know, appropriate for the occasion. You know, something that shows our care. You know, something, I don't know, something, well, you know, something hip."
msgstr "What, you daft? I can't just give her any old thing. You know, it is our leather anniversary after all. Why, it would have to be something, you know, appropriate for the occasion. You know, something that shows our care. You know, something, I don't know, something, well, you know, something hip."

