msgid "What song did the sheriff listen to over and over?"
msgstr "What song did the sheriff listen to over and over?"

#: 92P0902
msgid "The sheriff fell asleep here? In the diner?"
msgstr "The sheriff fell asleep here? In the diner?"

#: 92P0903
msgid "So you broke the records to get rid of the sheriff?"
msgstr "So you broke the records to get rid of the sheriff?"

