msgid "I should get going now."
msgstr "I should get going now."

#: 951F001
msgid "I'm on a bus!"
msgstr "I'm on a bus!"

#: 951F002
msgid "You got it, boss!"
msgstr "You got it, boss!"

#: 951Z001
msgid "There's the last three. Over there on that ridge. I'm on him, boss."
msgstr "There's the last three. Over there on that ridge. I'm on him, boss."

#: 951Z002
msgid "Well, our work is done, Flummox. Lay in a course for HQ. You got it, boss."
msgstr "Well, our work is done, Flummox. Lay in a course for HQ. You got it, boss."

#: 952Z001
msgid "Oh, for crying out loud, just use the hose on him!"
msgstr "Oh, for crying out loud, just use the hose on him!"

#: 955F001
msgid "Huh? Sorry, boss."
msgstr "Huh? Sorry, boss."

#: 955N001
msgid "It takes a lot of food to satisfy the hunger of an entire galaxy."
msgstr "It takes a lot of food to satisfy the hunger of an entire galaxy."

#: 955Z001
msgid "I'll be in my quarters reviewing the reconnaissance data. Don't disturb me until we get to ert!"
msgstr "I'll be in my quarters reviewing the reconnaissance data. Don't disturb me until we get to ert!"

#: 955Z002
msgid "FLUMMAGES! Sorry, boss. The clutch slipped."
msgstr "FLUMMAGES! Sorry, boss. The clutch slipped."

#: 956V001
msgid "Another fine harvest, Zlog. You ought to be congratulated. Fine harvest? Look, they're all skin and bones! I'm barely meeting my protein quota here!"
msgstr "Another fine harvest, Zlog. You ought to be congratulated. Fine harvest? Look, they're all skin and bones! I'm barely meeting my protein quota here!"

#: 956Z002
msgid "These stupid body-pooping activists!"
msgstr "These stupid body-pooping activists!"

#: 956Z003
msgid "What? Still unloading?"
msgstr "What? Still unloading?"

#: 957V001
msgid "It's no wonder you're a Ryan Burger's top protein procurement agent. You're always worrying about your quota."
msgstr "It's no wonder you're a Ryan Burger's top protein procurement agent. You're always worrying about your quota."

#: 957V002
msgid "Come."
msgstr "Come."

#: 957V003
msgid "Perhaps this next assignment will be more lucrative for you."
msgstr "Perhaps this next assignment will be more lucrative for you."

#: 957V004
msgid "The planet is called Earth. Preliminary analysis indicates a high likelihood of harvestability."
msgstr "The planet is called Earth. Preliminary analysis indicates a high likelihood of harvestability."

