msgstr "Do... very well."

#: 957Z001Z
msgid "But I have a feeling that this human will flunk with flying colors!"
msgstr "But I have a feeling that this human will flunk with flying colors!"

#: 958V001
msgid "And this will be your test specimen."
msgstr "And this will be your test specimen."

#: 958V002
msgid "I agree. But some nosy alien rights activists have been poking around and accusing us of harvesting intelligent life forms."
msgstr "I agree. But some nosy alien rights activists have been poking around and accusing us of harvesting intelligent life forms."

#: 958V003
msgid "I know, Slug. But as long as they're watching our every move, we simply cannot risk getting caught harvesting intelligent lifeforms."
msgstr "I know, Slug. But as long as they're watching our every move, we simply cannot risk getting caught harvesting intelligent lifeforms."

#: 958V004
msgid "The out specimen must be tested."
msgstr "The out specimen must be tested."

#: 958Z001
msgid "Look at him. There can't be much of a brain inside that puny skull. Testing this creature for intelligence would CLEARLY be a waste of time!"
msgstr "Look at him. There can't be much of a brain inside that puny skull. Testing this creature for intelligence would CLEARLY be a waste of time!"

#: 958Z002
msgid "Oh, but it's the smart ones that give our burgers their mouth, water, and flavor!"
msgstr "Oh, but it's the smart ones that give our burgers their mouth, water, and flavor!"

#: 959F001
msgid "I don't know how to do this."
msgstr "I don't know how to do this."

#: 959F002
msgid "There is a slight delay. A fat one got jammed in the protein transfer tube. I'm just finishing up now."
msgstr "There is a slight delay. A fat one got jammed in the protein transfer tube. I'm just finishing up now."

#: 959Z001
msgid "FLAMES!"
msgstr "FLAMES!"

#: 959Z002
msgid "Why aren't we unloaded yet?"
msgstr "Why aren't we unloaded yet?"

#: 959Z003
msgid "Well then, let's get this meat wagon moving! We got another job to do!"
msgstr "Well then, let's get this meat wagon moving! We got another job to do!"

#: 960W001
msgid "Please, don't eat me!"
msgstr "Please, don't eat me!"

#: 971D001
msgid "I'll do that right away. I used to have one, but the wheels fell off. Do you have a bigger glass? Oh yeah, it's the same. It's the same, but it's the same in my house. Hey! You want to watch where you're going, okay?"
msgstr "I'll do that right away. I used to have one, but the wheels fell off. Do you have a bigger glass? Oh yeah, it's the same. It's the same, but it's the same in my house. Hey! You want to watch where you're going, okay?"

